{"tid":1577521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 9.15死人求FC","createTime":"2019-09-17T17:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T17:59:33.000Z","uid":323889,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"930b819ee63b1010bcda5e5eb91f020e5cc7df77","tid":1577521,"uid":323889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"時間係9月15日大約凌晨12點幾<br />\n地點係北角英皇道 集友銀行出邊<br />\n<br />\n本身都幾靜 突然間好嘈 就去望下 <br />\n見到有狗打人 好快兩三分鐘後有個人瞓低咗<br />\n班狗係個人上面蓋左塊黑布 <br />\n當時第一下反應覺得<br />\n有人死咗所以先要蓋住黑布<br />\n<br />\n當時班狗係咁推進 叫啲記者走 <br />\n雖然得一張相 仲要咁低清 <br />\n但係搵緊直播去證明<br />\n真係有呢件事發生過  可惜暫時未搵到<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇記者朋友或者街坊記得有呢幕 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjMxpsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrjMxpsZ.jpg&h=7bbfef66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b6d9a397318457035c371a543d9df3a679485d5","tid":1577521,"uid":87852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:40:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8b5f49e0f3f778c00cfd7917a9ae520cd794022d","tid":1577521,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cacc1c84bf5c77649a0529f517f82c1377efeb08","tid":1577521,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"推到有真相"},{"pid":"5067760938ddf818c6e5a6f4ba8f2b5bb15c02ea","tid":1577521,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"推到有真相"},{"pid":"06cbcbf9274847bd1bd7ae1b44acdc37fbea9fff","tid":1577521,"uid":336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:41:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"366bc9487ea1d1b68a7715ab5d0ff5ad6256626c","tid":1577521,"uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:42:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4edf5401fe0c47a4c22d6e3126e5c05b038f68cb","tid":1577521,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0